title: Most valuable Swedish brands 2019
summary: This chart shows the Value of million made by Swedish in a brands 2019 .
\\n From the chart we see that the Volvo Swedish was the Most valuable Swedish in the 2019 with 21531 million .
The next Swedish to make the most million was the Nordea Swedish with 5638 million closely followed by the Absolut Swedish with 2404 million .
gold: As of 2019 , the self-assembly furniture retailer IKEA was the most valuable Swedish brand . The company 's value amounted to over 21 billion U.S. dollars that year . H & M ( short for Hennes & Mauritz ) came second , with a value of nearly 16 billion U.S. dollars .
